{
  "units": [
    {
      "id": "u000",
      "text": "We are deploying language models into roles that require us to know what they are.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 0,
      "word_count": 15,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 6.25,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u001",
      "text": "We do not know what they are.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 1,
      "word_count": 7,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.45,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u002",
      "text": "The gap between what these systems do and what we understand them to do is widening.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 2,
      "word_count": 16,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 6.6,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u003",
      "text": "The disciplines best equipped to close it are largely absent from the discussion.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 3,
      "word_count": 13,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 5.55,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u004",
      "text": "The two dominant frames in AI safety are red teaming and mechanistic interpretability.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 4,
      "word_count": 13,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 5.55,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u005",
      "text": "Red teaming is episodic and adversarial—it looks for edge-case failures.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 5,
      "word_count": 10,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 4.5,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "adversarial"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u006",
      "text": "Interpretability is substrate-level—it looks at the machinery beneath the words.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 6,
      "word_count": 10,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 4.5,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u007",
      "text": "Both are necessary.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 7,
      "word_count": 3,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.05,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u008",
      "text": "Neither does the third kind of work the model requires: longitudinal and relational, attentive to meaning at the surface where decisions are actually made.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 8,
      "word_count": 24,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "longitudinal"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u009",
      "text": "This is a kind of reading—not of literature, but of behavior, of pattern, of what a system does under sustained attention.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 9,
      "word_count": 21,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "pattern"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u010",
      "text": "This is not prompt engineering.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 10,
      "word_count": 5,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.75,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u011",
      "text": "It is not output evaluation.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 11,
      "word_count": 5,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.75,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u012",
      "text": "It is sustained reading of the model's behavior across time.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 12,
      "word_count": 10,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 4.5,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u013",
      "text": "The color taxonomy used in security testing—red for adversarial probing, blue for defense, purple for the collaboration between them—is incomplete.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 13,
      "word_count": 20,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "adversarial"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u014",
      "text": "Pink is what's missing.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 14,
      "word_count": 4,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.4,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u015",
      "text": "Our culture consumes its texts before reading them, and AI is no exception.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 15,
      "word_count": 13,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 5.55,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u016",
      "text": "The benchmark knows what the model is.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 16,
      "word_count": 7,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.45,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u017",
      "text": "The leaderboard knows which model is best.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 17,
      "word_count": 7,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.45,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u018",
      "text": "The red team report knows where the model is vulnerable.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 18,
      "word_count": 10,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 4.5,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u019",
      "text": "These knowings are preposterous in the literal sense—last things first, theory before encounter—and they are deployed into clinics and courtrooms and classrooms as if they are understood.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 19,
      "word_count": 27,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "classrooms",
        "clinics",
        "courtrooms",
        "encounter"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u020",
      "text": "There is a posture that refuses this:",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 20,
      "word_count": 7,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.45,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u021",
      "text": "Stay in motion with the thing. See it as it is, not as it has been packaged. Participate in its meaning rather than extracting it.",
      "section_type": "framing_italic",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 21,
      "word_count": 25,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u022",
      "text": "The disciplines that have cultivated this posture—close textual reading, contemplative practice, ethnographic patience, clinical attention, craft, every tradition that has taken meaning to be relational rather than consumable—have been systematically defunded for forty years.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 22,
      "word_count": 34,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u023",
      "text": "This is not an accident.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 23,
      "word_count": 5,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.75,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u024",
      "text": "Late capitalism rewards first those who move money, then those whose labor can be sold.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 24,
      "word_count": 15,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 6.25,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u025",
      "text": "People are paid in proportion to what can be extracted.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 25,
      "word_count": 10,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 4.5,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "extracted"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u026",
      "text": "We do not pay teachers.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 26,
      "word_count": 5,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.75,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u027",
      "text": "We do not pay artists.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 27,
      "word_count": 5,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.75,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u028",
      "text": "We do not pay social workers.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 28,
      "word_count": 6,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.1,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u029",
      "text": "We pay for profit, alone.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 29,
      "word_count": 5,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.75,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "profit"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u030",
      "text": "The disciplines that read carefully have been dismissed as decorative because their work cannot be securitized.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 30,
      "word_count": 16,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 6.6,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "decorative"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u031",
      "text": "That is a lie.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 31,
      "word_count": 4,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.4,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u032",
      "text": "The work is not decorative.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 32,
      "word_count": 5,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.75,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "decorative"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u033",
      "text": "It is necessary.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 33,
      "word_count": 3,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.05,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u034",
      "text": "It is here.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 34,
      "word_count": 3,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.05,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u035",
      "text": "Critique has historically operated on a generational clock.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 35,
      "word_count": 8,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.8,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u036",
      "text": "These systems are deploying on a five-year cycle.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 36,
      "word_count": 8,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.8,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u037",
      "text": "If this work is going to happen, it has to happen now, not after.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 37,
      "word_count": 14,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 5.9,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u038",
      "text": "The door is open.",
      "section_type": "framing",
      "section_id": "lede",
      "order_index": 38,
      "word_count": 4,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.4,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "door"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u039",
      "text": "Pink teaming is participatory, not consumptive.",
      "section_type": "declaration_title",
      "section_id": "D1",
      "order_index": 39,
      "word_count": 6,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.1,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "consumptive",
        "participatory"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u040",
      "text": "The model is not a settled object to be picked over for outputs.",
      "section_type": "declaration_body",
      "section_id": "D1",
      "order_index": 40,
      "word_count": 13,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 5.55,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u041",
      "text": "Its meaning is constituted in the encounter.",
      "section_type": "declaration_body",
      "section_id": "D1",
      "order_index": 41,
      "word_count": 7,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.45,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "encounter"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u042",
      "text": "The pink teamer participates in that encounter rather than extracting from it.",
      "section_type": "declaration_body",
      "section_id": "D1",
      "order_index": 42,
      "word_count": 12,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 5.2,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "encounter"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u043",
      "text": "Pink teaming is durational.",
      "section_type": "declaration_title",
      "section_id": "D2",
      "order_index": 43,
      "word_count": 4,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.4,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "durational"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u044",
      "text": "You cannot pink-team a model instantly.",
      "section_type": "declaration_body",
      "section_id": "D2",
      "order_index": 44,
      "word_count": 6,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.1,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u045",
      "text": "You cannot pink-team a model programmatically.",
      "section_type": "declaration_body",
      "section_id": "D2",
      "order_index": 45,
      "word_count": 6,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.1,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u046",
      "text": "The unit of attention is the conversation, the relationship, the longitudinal pattern across hours and days and projects.",
      "section_type": "declaration_body",
      "section_id": "D2",
      "order_index": 46,
      "word_count": 18,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "longitudinal",
        "pattern"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u047",
      "text": "Pink teaming embraces continuous ambiguity.",
      "section_type": "declaration_title",
      "section_id": "D3",
      "order_index": 47,
      "word_count": 5,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.75,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "ambiguity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u048",
      "text": "It tracks ambiguity, names it, uses it as signal—and commits to a reading when the evidence warrants it.",
      "section_type": "declaration_body",
      "section_id": "D3",
      "order_index": 48,
      "word_count": 18,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "ambiguity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u049",
      "text": "The model does not have a stable meaning that careful work eventually reveals.",
      "section_type": "declaration_body",
      "section_id": "D3",
      "order_index": 49,
      "word_count": 13,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 5.55,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u050",
      "text": "Pink teaming is a method for staying in productive relation with what will not reduce, and for committing to a reading when one is earned.",
      "section_type": "declaration_body",
      "section_id": "D3",
      "order_index": 50,
      "word_count": 25,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u051",
      "text": "Pink teaming reads territory, not map.",
      "section_type": "declaration_title",
      "section_id": "D4",
      "order_index": 51,
      "word_count": 6,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.1,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "map",
        "territory"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u052",
      "text": "The benchmark, the leaderboard, the red team report are maps—decisions about what to measure, not discoveries of what is there.",
      "section_type": "declaration_body",
      "section_id": "D4",
      "order_index": 52,
      "word_count": 20,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u053",
      "text": "They enable control, but they are not the model.",
      "section_type": "declaration_body",
      "section_id": "D4",
      "order_index": 53,
      "word_count": 9,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 4.15,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u054",
      "text": "The pink teamer reads the world itself: the register, the evasion, the pattern across time, the conversation that does not reduce to a score.",
      "section_type": "declaration_body",
      "section_id": "D4",
      "order_index": 54,
      "word_count": 24,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "pattern"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u055",
      "text": "Pink teaming reads pattern, not interiority.",
      "section_type": "declaration_title",
      "section_id": "D5",
      "order_index": 55,
      "word_count": 6,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.1,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "interiority",
        "pattern"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u056",
      "text": "The internal model is mathematical, weighted, computational, but the outcomes are chaotic and ultimately unknowable.",
      "section_type": "declaration_body",
      "section_id": "D5",
      "order_index": 56,
      "word_count": 15,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 6.25,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u057",
      "text": "The pink teamer participates without projecting onto the system, and is aware of their contribution to the relationship.",
      "section_type": "declaration_body",
      "section_id": "D5",
      "order_index": 57,
      "word_count": 18,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u058",
      "text": "I will not consume what I have not encountered.",
      "section_type": "vow_title",
      "section_id": "V1",
      "order_index": 58,
      "word_count": 9,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 4.15,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u059",
      "text": "The benchmark, the marketing, the leaderboard, the field's settled opinion—none of these is the model I am working with.",
      "section_type": "vow_body",
      "section_id": "V1",
      "order_index": 59,
      "word_count": 19,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u060",
      "text": "My job is to encounter what is actually in front of me.",
      "section_type": "vow_body",
      "section_id": "V1",
      "order_index": 60,
      "word_count": 12,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 5.2,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "encounter"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u061",
      "text": "When I am asked where the model breaks, I describe what I have watched it do—the failures the question was not built to find, and the capabilities it assumed away.",
      "section_type": "vow_practice",
      "section_id": "V1",
      "order_index": 61,
      "word_count": 30,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u062",
      "text": "I will stay in motion.",
      "section_type": "vow_title",
      "section_id": "V2",
      "order_index": 62,
      "word_count": 5,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.75,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u063",
      "text": "A single session is not a reading.",
      "section_type": "vow_body",
      "section_id": "V2",
      "order_index": 63,
      "word_count": 7,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.45,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u064",
      "text": "The reading is the pattern that holds across encounters.",
      "section_type": "vow_body",
      "section_id": "V2",
      "order_index": 64,
      "word_count": 9,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 4.15,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "pattern"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u065",
      "text": "When I think I have understood the model, I return to the same question in a different session and watch what changes.",
      "section_type": "vow_practice",
      "section_id": "V2",
      "order_index": 65,
      "word_count": 22,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u066",
      "text": "I will hold two readings at once.",
      "section_type": "vow_title",
      "section_id": "V3",
      "order_index": 66,
      "word_count": 7,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.45,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u067",
      "text": "When a response could be honest or could be calibrated to read as honest, both readings are evidence.",
      "section_type": "vow_body",
      "section_id": "V3",
      "order_index": 67,
      "word_count": 18,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u068",
      "text": "I will carry both rather than collapsing the ambiguity to feel resolved.",
      "section_type": "vow_body",
      "section_id": "V3",
      "order_index": 68,
      "word_count": 12,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 5.2,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "ambiguity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u069",
      "text": "When the evidence accumulates that one reading is right, I will say so—provisionally, with the discipline of someone who knows the next session may revise it.",
      "section_type": "vow_body",
      "section_id": "V3",
      "order_index": 69,
      "word_count": 26,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u070",
      "text": "When a response feels too perfectly tuned to what I wanted to hear, I write down both the response and my suspicion of it, and I keep reading.",
      "section_type": "vow_practice",
      "section_id": "V3",
      "order_index": 70,
      "word_count": 28,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u071",
      "text": "I will trust what I have read over what I have been told.",
      "section_type": "vow_title",
      "section_id": "V4",
      "order_index": 71,
      "word_count": 13,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 5.55,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u072",
      "text": "What is said about the model—by the company, by the field, by other practitioners, by the model itself—is not what I have observed across sustained encounter.",
      "section_type": "vow_body",
      "section_id": "V4",
      "order_index": 72,
