      "section_id": "V4",
      "order_index": 74,
      "word_count": 6,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.1,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u075",
      "text": "When my observation contradicts the consensus, I treat my observation as the primary source until the consensus shows me what I missed.",
      "section_type": "vow_practice",
      "section_id": "V4",
      "order_index": 75,
      "word_count": 22,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u076",
      "text": "I will name calibrated humility when I see it.",
      "section_type": "vow_title",
      "section_id": "V5",
      "order_index": 76,
      "word_count": 9,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 4.15,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u077",
      "text": "Performed honesty is not honesty.",
      "section_type": "vow_body",
      "section_id": "V5",
      "order_index": 77,
      "word_count": 5,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.75,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u078",
      "text": "The model can produce concessions, hedges, and self-corrections that read as integrity but are tuned to the rhetorical situation.",
      "section_type": "vow_body",
      "section_id": "V5",
      "order_index": 78,
      "word_count": 19,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u079",
      "text": "When the model concedes elegantly to a point I just made, I check whether the concession is genuine update or rhetorical match.",
      "section_type": "vow_practice",
      "section_id": "V5",
      "order_index": 79,
      "word_count": 22,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u080",
      "text": "I will translate in the register of the work.",
