      "section_id": "V6",
      "order_index": 80,
      "word_count": 9,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 4.15,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u081",
      "text": "When a clinician, lawyer, founder, or teacher asks what the model can do, I will answer in the language of the decision they are actually making, not the language of the demo.",
      "section_type": "vow_body",
      "section_id": "V6",
      "order_index": 81,
      "word_count": 32,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u082",
      "text": "I will underclaim before I overclaim.",
      "section_type": "vow_body",
      "section_id": "V6",
      "order_index": 82,
      "word_count": 6,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 3.1,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u083",
      "text": "When I am asked whether the model can do something, I describe what I have watched it do and what I have watched it fail at, in the asker's terms, not the field's.",
