      "section_id": "V7",
      "order_index": 86,
      "word_count": 5,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 2.75,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u087",
      "text": "When I write or speak about this work, I read it back and cut every term that requires the discipline I came from.",
      "section_type": "vow_practice",
      "section_id": "V7",
      "order_index": 87,
      "word_count": 23,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u088",
      "text": "Every model deployed in production is deployed on the basis of decisions about what it can do, what it is for, and where its limits are.",
