      "section_id": "closing",
      "order_index": 90,
      "word_count": 14,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 5.9,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u091",
      "text": "Pink teaming offers a frame, and offers it to the people best equipped to use it.",
      "section_type": "closing_framing",
      "section_id": "closing",
      "order_index": 91,
      "word_count": 16,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 6.6,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u092",
      "text": "If you have spent your life cultivating sustained attention to systems whose meaning will not hold still—by whatever tradition, in whatever discipline, under whatever name—your training is more relevant to this moment than you have been told.",
      "section_type": "closing_framing",
      "section_id": "closing",
      "order_index": 92,
      "word_count": 37,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u093",
      "text": "The work is yours if you have the posture.",
      "section_type": "closing_framing",
      "section_id": "closing",
      "order_index": 93,
      "word_count": 9,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 4.15,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u094",
      "text": "The pink teamer is responsible to the people who will be affected by what the model does in deployment—the patient, the defendant, the student, the reader.",
