      "section_id": "closing",
      "order_index": 94,
      "word_count": 26,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u095",
      "text": "The work answers to them, not to the model and not to the lab.",
      "section_type": "closing_framing",
      "section_id": "closing",
      "order_index": 95,
      "word_count": 14,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 5.9,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u096",
      "text": "The future of knowledge work, of education, of the relationship between humans and machines, is humanistic and relational.",
      "section_type": "closing_framing",
      "section_id": "closing",
      "order_index": 96,
      "word_count": 18,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 7.0,
      "contains_keywords": []
    },
    {
      "id": "u097",
      "text": "The disciplines that read closely, hold ambiguity, and attend to surfaces are the disciplines this moment needs.",
      "section_type": "closing_framing",
      "section_id": "closing",
      "order_index": 97,
      "word_count": 17,
      "expected_dwell_seconds": 6.95,
      "contains_keywords": [
        "ambiguity"
      ]
    },
    {
